Amber Heard was spotted tooling around town in the pricy Tesla that her ex-boyfriend Elon Musk gave her back when they were dating. 
The new mother, 35, was seen running errands in Santa Monica, California on Tuesday cruising in her sleek black electric car from the billionaire's auto company. 
Heard and Musk dated for roughly a year back in 2018 following the end of her tumultuous marriage to actor Johnny Depp.
